Description:
    Creates a new pixi-plugin.

Example:
    yo pixi-plugin

    This will create:
        gulp/tasks: Gulp build tasks
        gulp/util: Gulp build utilities
        src/: JavaScript source (CommonJS files built with pixi-plugin)

        .editorconfig: editor configuration file
        .gitignore: git ignore files
        .jshintrc: jshint configuration

        gulpfile.js: Configuration and bootstrap for the task runner.
        package.json: Package descriptor.
        README.md: Your application's README file.
        LICENSE: Your application's license file.
        CONTRIBUTING.md: A contribution guide for your project.
